The one image that works (hero-jumper.png) is correctly referenced as .png in your code.
The Fix
Open your page component file — based on the Next.js structure, it's at src/app/page.tsx — and change all 5 .jpg references to .png. Specifically, find and replace these:
hero-team-bg.jpg   →   hero-team-bg.png
court-tactics.jpg  →   court-tactics.png
arena-gear.jpg     →   arena-gear.png
arena-match.jpg    →   arena-match.png
arena-drills.jpg   →   arena-drills.png
A quick way to do this in VS Code: open src/app/page.tsx, press Ctrl+H (Find and Replace
